| [GIA 1ct G-VS2 Round](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29112616?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | Round | G-VS2 Excellent | $3,370 | No bow-tie, GIA cut verified |
| [GIA 1ct G-VS1 Round](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29161966?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | Round | G-VS1 Excellent | $3,300 | Best value entry for round |
